    "Edit `settings.json` directly. Limpid watches the file and reloads on save. A typo is recoverable — the malformed copy is renamed to settings.json.bak-decode-failed-<ts> on the next launch and defaults are loaded.": {
      "comment": "Advanced pane settings.json section footer",
